subject re geico goldberg oasi dt navi mil mark goldberg write in rec auto jmh hopper virginia edu jeffrei hoffmeist write my suggest stai where you ar or shop around but stai awai from geico i strongli agre with jeff here s my horror stori mani year back i switch to geico from state farm to save some i have a rel new sport car for which we cover with liabil collis and comprehens with thi make of car new model came out in januari not septemb like other make the car wa purchas in august of that year we also had a much older clunker for which we onli want liabil low and behold a vandal slash the roof of the sport car and we put in a claim thi wa in octob still the current model year for the car a new top with instal wa we had deduct so we should have gotten you had to go to geico s local offic to have an adjust see the car unlik state farm that sent the adjust to the shop or your place he said sinc the car is now on year old we ll depreci the top by so you ll get on the claim thi will also count as an accid against you so your rate mai increas the hassl continu then we got a letter from geico sai claim deni your polici on thi car doesn t cover thi i then learn that their record had the full coverag collis etc on our old clunker and onli had liabil for thi new car thei mix up our car in their record i fix the top myself with some carpet thread and drop my claim thei still charg me with an accid i cancel my polici and switch to anoth compani the coup de gra came when thei sent me a bill for an addit balanc due for the differ in collis comprehens cost between my sport car and my clunker i return the bill unpaid with a nastygram plu explic direct to perform recto cranial insert haven t heard from them sinc everyon s entitl to my opinion goldberg oasi dt navi mil imagin is more import than knowledg albert einstein good for you i am convinc that someon should start a boycott against geico ani taker chintan amin the univers of illinoi urbanachampaign mail llama uiuc edu sig 